\p \k Agelo\k* in nanm…®n yame ramarha tuk yermam…ô. Wok kap…ôri…ô in e kamhani-…ôrhav n…ôgkiarien kape Kughen tuk narmam…ô kape Kughen m…®n…ô. Agelo khapsaah, yame rhuv…ô k…®rik, yame raha k…®rik. Yame raha kamni k…®m…ô yarmh…ô, kasoriah n…®mraghien kape narmam…ô.
\p \k Aposol\k* in yermam…ô k…®rik r…ômhen k…®n kamher-p…ôn k…®n. Yesu r…®m…®rpen narmam…ô twelef kafan m…®n…ô m…ô tukhau…ô iri…ô aposol tuk norien merekel m…®ne n…®ni-…ôrhavyen n…ôgkiarien kafan (Mat 10:1-4; Mak 3:13-19; Luk 6:12-16). In apa kupan, k…®m…®ni aposol r…ômhen k…®n narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®m…®s…ôm Yesu m…®s…ôriw…ôk iri…ô min m…®s…ôm n…®mh…ôyen kafan ye kros. Yesu r…®m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn nehu…ôyen k…®mi Pol m…ô Pol r…®mn…ôm In ye n…ômr…ôrhavyen k…®ni Yesu rokr…ôn k…®n in m…ô in aposol m…®n k…®rik kafan.
\p \k Farisi\k* k…®s…ômhen k…®n pati k…®rik. Iri…ô k…®s…ômhen k…®n n…ômehu…ô kape n…ôm…ô Isrel. Iri…ô narmam…ô t…®ks…®n yam…ô m…®ne kharkun huv…ô loa, mas…ôri-p…ôn, mamharp…®n. Yesu r…®p…ôh norkeikeiyen …ôri…ô meinai iri…ô kas…ôs…®k …ôpnis loa kape Kughen, k…®ni mhav…ôhsi-hakt…ô atuk …ôri…ô m…ô iri…ô k…®s…ôri-p…ôn huv…ô loa. Pati mir a Farisi m…®ne Sadusi, kamhani m…ô iri…ô n…ômhajoun m…®n…ô kape loa.
\p \k Fig\k* in nai k…®rik yame kam…ôn kw…ônkwan. N…®mar…®n r…ômhen k…®n malberi, m…ôr…®g kw…ônkwan r…ômhen k…®n kw…ônimh, m…ôr…®g in rheik…ôn.
\p \k Gol\k* in kapier okr…ô k…®rik yame ramser-ser p…®k, m…ôrir. Kamor nar…®mnar r…®psaah k…®n yame n…®mr…®n rhakt…ô, r…ômhen k…®n ring m…®ne earring u…ô kwenar yame kam…ôkwan.
\p \k Grep, plantesen kape grep\k* Grep in kw…ônkwai nai k…®rik, t…®ks…®n r…ômr…ômr…ô, t…®ks…®n r…ôwhao. Kamor waen k…®n. Kw…ônkwan r…ômhen k…®n pi. Ramerko r…ômhen k…®n n…ôr…ôus.
\p \k Hae pris\k* in yermam…ô k…®rik yame ram…ôrhak…ô. In rav…ôh nar m…®ragh mavi n…®t…ô mamor sakrefaes k…®n m…ô Kughen tukr…®v…ôhsi-ta narp…®nien kape t…ôvhag…ô has kape narmam…ô. Newk m…®n…ô fam kasarukun daes tukun m…ô pa nhag…®n e ye pris m…®n…ô a in tukru…ô mamor wok kape hae pris kape newk k…®rikian…ô.
\p \k Herod\k*Niutestamen ramvsao k…®n narmam…ô kuas nhagri…ô e Herod.
\pi1 1. \it Herod Ehu…ô\it* in king kape provins e Judia n…®p…®g Yesu r…®mnarha-p…ô. In e r…®m…ô tukhopni Yesu ye n…®p…®g yame r…®mnarha iran (Mat 2:1-22; Luk 1:5).
\pi1 2. \it Herod Antipas\it* in ji Herod Ehu…ô yame r…®mnamaru ye n…®p…®g Yesu r…®mnarha. In r…®mnamaru ye tan…ô e Galili ye n…®p…®g a Yesu r…®namor wok mamni-…ôrhav n…ôgkiarien kape Kughen iran. In e in r…®m…®k…®r ta piraov…®n kape piauni Filip, nhag…®n e Herodias. K…®ni n…®p…®g Jon Baptaes r…®m…®ni-…ôhu in m…ô tukr…®p…ôh n…®k…®rien Herodias, r…®mn…ôr…ôru ta kapan kap…ô Jon Baptaes (Mak 6:14-29). N…®p…®g n…ôm…ô Isrel k…®m…®s…ôr…®p Yesu ye kot, Herod Antipas e in e r…®m…®ni m…ô Yesu tukram…ôkeikei m…®mh…ô.
\pi1 3. \it Herod Agripa K…®rikian…ô\it* in ji Aristopolas e in piau Herod Antipas. In r…®mnor ahas p…ôn k…®mi aposol m…®n…ô n…®p…®g Yesu r…®mamh…ô mamragh m…®n mamv…ôn ye rao ye neai. Mhopni Jemes e piau Jon. In a r…®mnausit p…®k, Kughen r…®mnor narp…®nien k…®min, ramamh…ô mim m…®n…ô k…®m…®s…ôn t…®peu…ô iran (Wok 12:1-23).
\pi1 4. \it Herod Agripa K…®raru\it* in ji Herod Agripa K…®rikian…ô. Herod a in a r…®mnamar…ô ye n…®p…®g kape Pol, mam…ôt…ôr…®g k…®n n…ôgkiarien kafan n…®p…®g r…®mn…ôrer ye kot kape Festas (Wok 25:13-26:2; 29:19, 27-32).
\p \k Hosana\k* In n…ôgkiarien akwas k…®rik kape n…ôm…ô Isrel. N…®pran ramni m…ô ‚ÄúHav…ôh si hakt…ô‚Äù u…ô ‚ÄúV…ôh m…®ragh.‚Äù
\p \k Ji yermam…ô\k* N…®pran r…®m…ô in yermam…ô …ôm…ô k…®rik. M…ôr…®g profet Esikel r…®m…®v…ôh nahag a mam…ôgkiar atuk iran. Yesu r…®v…ôh nahag a mamor m…ô in yemehu…ô k…®rik r…ômhen k…®n Profet Esikel kupan.
\p \k Kaonsel\k* kas…ôkir n…ôgkiarien apa kot.
\p \k Kot\k* In nar k…®rik yame ram…ôkir n…ôgkiarien kape narmam…ô m…ô rameiku…ô u…ô ram…ôfrah. M…®v…ôh-si-p…ôn narp…®nien k…®mi narmam…ô tuk nakap…®rien loa.
\p \k Kristo\k* in nahag. Ye n…ôgkiarien kape n…ôm…ô Gris, n…®pran e ramni m…®m…ô ‚Äúyermam…ô yame Kughen r…®m…®rpen m…ô tukrher-p…ô k…®n m…ô tukr…®v…ôh m…®ragh narmam…ô.‚Äù N…ôm…ô Isrel k…®mnhawhin kw…ôn a Kristo m…ô tukru…ô, k…®s…ôm m…ô pa e nhag…®n in Kristo. N…ôm…ô Isrel khapsaah kham…ô p…ôh nien m…ô Yesu in Kristo, meinai k…®s…ôm m…ô Yesu in yermam…ô apnap…®g …ôm…ô, kafan nar k…®rik r…®k…ôk. M…ôr…®g nar…ôyen kape Yesu r…®mnor n…ôgkiarien m…®n…ô kape profet tu m…®n…ô r…®mau…ô m…®nor n…ôfrak…®sien k…®n, ramhajoun p…ôn m…ô Yesu in Kristo.
\p \k Leprosi\k* in n…ômh…ôyen k…®rik yame ror yermam…ô r…ômhir-…ômhir, t…®kin ram…ôta. Tukm…ô yermam…ô rav…ôh n…ômh…ôyen a leprosi m…ôrer ipak…ô tuk yermam…ô k…®rik, r…®rkun n…®v…ôhsi-p…ônien k…®mi yermam…ô ai. Ror p…ôn k…®n narmam…ô kamhag…®n p…®k k…®n n…ômh…ôyen a leprosi m…ô in n…ômh…ôyen …ôut…ôn.
\p \k Lifaet\k* in k…®rik ye kw…ôn…ôr…ôus twelef kape n…ôm…ô Isrel. Laen …ôm…ô kape Lifaet in p…®s…®n …ôm…ô r…®rkun nu…ôyen m…ô pris.
\p \k Loa kape Moses\k* ramni ye n…ôkw…ôkw…ô k…®rk…®r…®p e Moses r…®m…®rai kupan ye Oltestamen: Jenesis, Eksodas, Levitikas, Namba m…®ne Dutronome.
\p \k Lugun apa Galili\k* in nu …ôgkap, m…ôr…®g ram…ôm…®r ye kwerkwan ye tan…ô apa Isrel, k…®ni rehu…ô p…®k, mavi r…ômhen k…®n tahik. Peao peao aik…®n kafan. Nahag p…®s…®n k…®rik e Lugun Taebirias (Jon 6:1) u…ô Lugun Genesaret (Luk 5:1). Nehu…ôyen kafan r…ômhen k…®n twenti tu kilometa.
\p \k Mesaea\k* in n…ôgkiarien kape n…ôm…ô Isrel n…®pran r…ômhen …ôm…ô k…®n Kristo, u…ô ‚Äúyermam…ô yame Kughen r…®m…®rpen m…ô tukrher-p…ô k…®n m…ô tukr…®v…ôh m…®ragh narmam…ô.‚Äù
\p \k Nanm…®n kape Kughen\k* in r…ômhen k…®n nanm…®n k…®rik yame ramor wok yerki yermam…ô. Kughen Yermaru, m…®ne Yesu Kristo, m…®ne Nanm…®n Rhak…ô, iris…®r k…®rikian…ô.
\p \k Narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne p…ôh nien m…ô kw…ôn…ôr…ôus kape n…ôm…ô Isrel\k* in translesen kape Inglis yame ramni m…ô ‚ÄúGentile.‚Äù Kupan, n…ôm…ô Isrel iri…ô kham…ô Kughen r…®m…®rpen …ôm…ô …ôri…ô m…ô iri…ô narmam…ô kafan m…®n…ô. Kham…ô iri…ô p…®s…®n …ôm…ô kharkun naha nhag…®n yame ratuatuk, mham…ô iri…ô p…®s…®n …ôm…ô kharkun Kughen. N…ôm…ô Isrel k…ôs…®g p…ôn narman mham…ô Kughen r…®m…®rpen …ôri…ô p…®s…®n …ôm…ô.
\p \k Narmaruyen kape Kughen\k* in translesen kape Inglis yame ramni m…ô ‚ÄúKingdom of God.‚Äù N…®pran k…®rik e narmam…ô tukhav…ôn m…®sar…ô iri…ô Kughen ye rao ye neai. K…®rik m…®n e Kughen tukrar…ô mehu…ô ye n…®mraghien kafam mhajoun ik k…®n swatuk.
\p \k N…ôv…®g…®nien Rhak…ô\k* in Lodsapa. Bred m…®ne waen yame n…ôm…ôhuak m…®n…ô kamhav…ôh, r…®kiri…ô ram…ôs…®k n…®mh…ôyen kape Yesu.
\p \k N…®kakien kape Kughen\k* In translesen kape Inglis yame ramni m…ô ‚ÄúGlori.‚Äù Ramhajoun p…ôn nehu…ôyen kape Kughen k…®ni mamor m…ô yermam…ô tukr…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn n…®siaiyen m…®v…ôh-si hakt…ô In.
\p \k Nim…ô Ehu…ô kape Kughen\k* in translesen kape Inglis yame ramni m…ô ‚ÄúTemple.‚Äù K…®ni in k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô, ye taon kape n…ôm…ô Isrel ye kapitol city Jerusalem. Hae pris m…®n…ô kape n…ôm…ô Isrel k…®m…®sor sakrefaes ye newk m…®n…ô fam aik…®n a. M…ôr…®g ye newk A.D. 70 mobael kape n…ôm…ô Rom k…®m…®sarkw…ôs…®s nim…ô a.
\p \k Nim…ô kape nofug…®nien kape n…ôm…ô Isrel\k* ror p…®s…®n ye nim…ô ehu…ô kape Kughen apa Jerusalem, meinai nim…ô kape nofug…®nien khapsaah ye taon p…®s…®n p…®s…®n. N…ômhajoun kape loa m…®n…ô k…®mnhav…ôh-si …ôrhav n…ôgkiarien aik…®n, m…ôr…®g khap…ôh n…®sorien sakrefaes aik…®n. M…ôr…®g nim…ô kape nofug…®nien kape n…ôm…ô Isrel r…®p…ôh n…ômhenien k…®n nim…ôhuak m…®n…ô ai taktakun, meinai n…ôm…ô Isrel khap…ôh nhaniyen n…ôfrak…®sien ye Yesu Kristo.
\p \k N…®p…®g Kwas…®g\k* n…®pran r…®m…ô n…®p…®g Kughen tukru…ô iran. Tukroriah tokrei tan…ô, mam…ôkir narmam…ô, m…®p…®k ta n…ôm…ôhuak m…®n…ô iri…ô tuksap mhav…ôn m…®sar…ô ye rao ye neai. K…®ni Kughen tukr…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne khap…ôh nhakwas…®gien k…®n in iri…ô Setan ye nap yame ramu…ôk rer…®n.
\p \k N…®rpenien wi\k* Apa kupan, swatuk kape n…®v…ôhsi-tayen narp…®nien kape t…ôvhag…ô has in e n…®viyen n…®taw nar m…®ragh. Kughen r…®mnor …ôpu norien a ye n…ôkw…ôkw…ô m…®ne kamni k…®m…ô Oltestamen. K…®ni In mor promes wi m…®m…ô norien kape n…®viyen n…®taw nar m…®ragh tukror infamien. N…®rpenien wi e ramni tukm…ô n…®m…®ni n…ôfrak…®sien ye Yesu Kristo, in r…®rkun n…®v…ôhsi-tayen narp…®nien kape t…ôvhag…ô has kafam. K…®mn…ôs…ôvheik…®n n…®rpenien wi e ye n…ôkw…ôkw…ô m…®ne kamni k…®m…ô Niutestamen.
\p \k Pasova\k* N…®p…®g Moses r…®mnamk…®r ye rhav narmam…ô kafan m…®n…ô ye kwerm…® Fero, agelo k…®rik kape Kughen r…®m…®v…ôh m…®ragh kw…ôn…ôr…ôus kape Moses. Ror p…ôn nahasien ru…ô, m…®vi-…ôrok…®n …ôri…ô. Mhopni fam n…®mr…® nupan m…®n…ô narman kape n…ôm…ô Ijip. M…ôr…®g n…ôm…ô Isrel k…®m…®s…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn n…®taw sipsip ye kw…ôru…ô, agelo r…ôm r…®rkun m…ô iri…ô k…®m…®sor n…ôgkiarien yame Moses r…®m…®ni, k…®ni in m…®vi-…ôro k…®n …ôri…ô. Ror p…ôn k…®n n…ôm…ô Isrel kasor n…®p…®g e Pasova ye newk m…®n…ô fam, masor n…ôv…®g…®nien ramuh p…ôn n…®p…®g a. (∆ém-ru stori kape Pasova ye Eks12:21-30).
\p \k Perel\k* in kapier huv…ô k…®rik yame ram…ôm…®r apa ye n…ôkwai nar k…®rik ye tahik r…ômhen k…®n kokias. N…®mr…®n rhakt…ô, kamor kwenar k…®n, m…®ne earring.
\p \k Profet\k* in yermam…ô k…®rik yame Kughen rav…ôhsi-p…ôn n…ôgkiarien k…®min m…ô nar k…®rik tukr…®t…ôrhav-p…ô mor n…ôfrak…®sien k…®n. Profet iri…ô m-fam twenti yam…ô m…®ne k…®mnharai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô m…®n…ô ye Oltestamen, r…®rikakun ye Aesaea, mor infamien ye Malakae. Mhani mham…® tukm…ô narmam…ô khap…ôh n…®s…ôri-p…ônien n…ôgkiarien kape Kughen, Kughen tukroriah nar…ôyen kap…ôri…ô. M…ôr…®g profet m…®n t…®ks…®n aik…®n yam…ô m…®ne k…®mnhaph nharaiyen n…ôkw…ôkw…ô.
\p \k Promes\k* n…®pran e n…®rpenien.
\p \k Sabat\k* Ye n…ôgkiarien kape n…ôm…ô Isrel, n…®pran ramni m…ô ‚Äúseven.‚Äù In n…®p…®g infamien kape wik, yame yermam…ô ramap…®s iran meinai Kughen r…®mnor nar…®mnar fam m…®v…ôh n…®p…®g sikis mamap…®s ye n…®p…®g yame ror seven k…®n. Sabat in n…®p…®g k…®rik kape n…ôm…ô Isrel kas…ôhuak iran. R…®rikakun ye Fraede sikis klok yenaiyu, mor infamien ye Sarure, sikis klok yenaiyu. N…®p…®g aposol m…®n…ô k…®mnhav…ôn apa kantri p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n…ô, n…ôm…ô ik…®n m…®n…ô a k…®mnhap…ôh nharkunien nar…ôyen kape n…ôm…ô Isrel, mhap…ôh n…®s…ôhuakien ye Sabat, k…®ni n…®p…®g k…®mnhau…ô mharkun Yesu, m…®s…ôhuak ye Sande meinai Yesu r…®m…®mragh m…®n ye n…®mh…ôyen kafan ye Sande.
\p \k Sadusi\k* iri…ô k…®s…ômhen k…®n pati k…®rik. Iri…ô k…®s…ômhen k…®n n…ômehu…ô kape n…ôm…ô Isrel. Iri…ô m…®n k…®m…®shajoun loa kape Moses. Iri…ô kham…ô tam…ô tukm…ô yermam…ô r…®mamh…ô, r…®nor infamien; nanm…®n to r…®p…ôh n…®v…ônien ik…®n k…®rik. Mhani m…®n m…ô agelo r…®k…ôk m…®ne yarmh…ô.
\p \k Saeon\k* in tukwas k…®rik yame k…®m…®vhir…ôk…®n-p…ôn Jerusalem ik…®n (Dut 4:48). Nhag…®n m…®n k…®rik e Heron. Ye n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e Hibrus, Saeon in ramuh p…ôn rao ye neai.
\p \k Sakrefaes\k* Yame k…®mnamor kupan narmam…ô k…®mnhav…ôhsi-p…ôn nar m…®ragh p…®s…®n p…®s…®n r…ômhen k…®n mak, kau, u…ô sipsip k…®mi hae pris m…®n…ô m…ô tukhavaan …ôru mhav…ôh tamhek t…ôvhag…ô has kap…ôri…ô. Sakrefaes m…®n k…®rik in e tuk n…®niyen tenkiu. M…ôr…®g tukm…ô nar m…®ragh yame ramh…ô u…ô yame rahas, to k…®p…ôh norien sakrefaes k…®n.
\p \k Sakomsaes\k* Kughen r…®m…®ni-p…ôn tuk Ebraham ye Jen 17 m…ô tukv…ôh nao k…®mi narman k…ôtu kar…®n …ôri…ô p…ôh kafan. Tukm…ô n…®p…®g yerman rarha m…®v…ôh n…®p…®g eit, k…®v…ôh nao k…®min ramuh p…ôn m…ô rav…ôh n…®huv…ôyen yame Kughen r…®m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn k…®mi Ebraham. M…ôr…®g Aposol Pol r…®mnhajoun m…ô norien kape sakomsaes r…®ukreik…®n ai taktakun. Sakomsaes to r…®p…ôh n…®v…ôhyen ik nakv…ôn ye rao ye neai, m…ôr…®g takni n…ôfrak…®sien ye Yesu Kristo, p…ôh Yesu ror sakomsaes k…®mik m…ôrai ta nahasien yerkim.
\p \k Setan\k* ye n…ôgkiarien kape n…ôm…ô Isrel, n…®pran ramni m…ô ‚Äút…®km…®r.‚Äù Setan in agelo k…®rik kape Kughen kupan yame r…®mnamor norien has m…®p…ôh n…®kwas…®gien k…®n n…ôr…®gien kape Kughen, Kughen rher-yerhav k…®n ye rao ye neai iri…ô kafan kwhen, k…®seiwaiyu-p…ô ye tokrei tan…ô (Aes 14:12-15; Esik 28:1-19; Mat 13:38-40; Luk 1:15; Jud 6, Rev 12).
\p \k Sinae\k* in tukwas k…®rik ye kantri apa Ijip. Kw…ônmhan a in a Kughen r…®m…®v…ôh-si p…ôn Natuak…ômien Ten k…®mi Moses ik…®n (Hib 12:18-24).
\p \k Sisa\k* pa r…®m…ô nhag yermam…ô m…ôr…®g in nehu…ôyen r…ômhen k…®n presiden. In yamehu…ô kape n…ôm…ô Rom. N…ôm…ô Rom kamhani mham…ô in …ôm…ô r…ômhen k…®n ji Kughen.
\p \k Slef\k* in yermam…ô k…®rik yame ramor wok …ôm…ô m…®p…ôh n…®v…ôhyen n…ôrok iran. Ramor wok …ôm…ô mam…ôri-p…ôn …ôm…ô n…ôr…®gien kape yemehu…ô kafan, m…ôr…®g r…®p…ôh n…ôri-p…ônien n…ôr…®gien kafan.
\p \k Wit\k* in nai k…®rik r…ômhen k…®n raes, kam…ôkwai-…ôkwai, kw…ônkwan ram…ôsaah, mam…ôp…ôh t…®kin. Kamarkin kw…ônkwan kamor flaoa k…®n.
\p \k Yalgita\k* in nar m…®ragh ehu…ô k…®rik rahas p…®k yame ram…ôm…®r ye n…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Revelesen. Ram…ôs yermam…ô.
